	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I agree with Dadiella (the prev post) I'm a 21 rogue on the Povar server, and if a rogue desperately needs to practice Safe fall, he should get a sow and run around in a hilly zone like dagnors cauldron, just on the run from GFAY to Unrest my skill usually maxes out (note you do need a sow to get the skill to go up this way, otherwise you aren't moving fast enough to get the extra drop off the hills and end up running down them)<br><br>Lerryn Twoblades<br>Arbiters of the Apocalypse<br>Povar Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
