	   <tr><td colspan=2>Actually becareful what you jump off off I jumped side of that big bridge connecting Iceclad to Eastern Wastes (trying to take a short cut, wasn't that big of a fall).&nbsp;&nbsp;Anyways I fell for 10,000 points of damage.  So be careful Kunark and Velius for some reason falling from lower heights cause quite a bit more damage.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
